title: nds4ios version 0.6 ipa
description:
Play your favorite nds games on your iphone or ipad.

For Jailbroken iPhones

1. install appsync on iPhone

2. add IPA file to itunes

3. sync app to iphone or ipad



This is not the most current version. But it is a working version until the app is back up on the hosts site.  If I find newer versions of the IPA, I will upload them also




Creator of nds4ios website http://angelxwind.net/
